article.description: — Richard Harward recorded 13 points and 11 rebounds to lead BYU to a 72-63 win over San Francisco on Saturday.
article.headline: Harward lifts BYU past San Francisco 72-63
article.linkText: Harward lifts BYU past San Francisco 72-63
article.story: SAN FRANCISCO -- — Richard Harward recorded 13 points and 11 rebounds to lead BYU to a 72-63 win over San Francisco on Saturday. Alex Barcello had 19 points for BYU (11-3, 2-1 West Coast Conference). Gideon George added 12 points. Caleb Lohner had seven rebounds. Khalil Shabazz had 30 points for the Dons (9-7, 3-3). Dzmitry Ryuny added 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
